<synopsis><code mime="text/x-python">
@accepts(cairo.Context, Clutter.Color)
@returns(none)
def cairo_set_source_color(cr, color)
</code></synopsis>
<p>Utility function for setting the source color of @cr using
a <link xref="Clutter.Color">Clutter.Color</link>. This function is the equivalent of:</p><p>|[
cairo_set_source_rgba (cr,
color-&gt;red / 255.0,
color-&gt;green / 255.0,
color-&gt;blue / 255.0,
color-&gt;alpha / 255.0);
]|</p>

